Ex-Big Brother Naija, BBNaija ‘double Wahala housemates have reacted to Mercy’s emergence as the winner of 2019 ‘Pepper Dem’ edition. Mercy floored other finalists, Mike, Seyi, Frodd and Omashola to win N60 million worth of prize. The season began broadcasting 99 days ago with 26 housemates. Big Brother Naija had its fourth season in Nigeria. Mercy is the first female to emerge winner of the show. Here are some reactions from ex-BBNaija housemates: @Leo Dasilva: “A very great season. Congratulations to everyone that participated and to the crew members. You all put on a great show.” @Khloe: “Lamborghini Mercynlord you are worthy of all our praise.” @Ifuenada “Confratilations to the first ever female winner of BBNaija, Mercy. You did it for all of us our efforts was not in vain.” @RicoSwarvey “Congratulations Lamborghini Mercy.” @Bambam “Big big Congratulations to the winner of this seasons show! Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.